You can't tell what these bones are from. Could be anything from fish, to sahuagin or humans. 

What you do know, is that whatever force snapped the bones like twigs, and appears to have eaten the poor creatures (judging by the tooth marks), would likely be a challenging opponent, should you have to defend yourself from it.
